		<div class="post-title">
			<h2 class="hero-header">Advising</h2>
		</div>
		
		 

		<!-- Begin Optional Content Blocks -->
		
        	<!-- Begin Description -->
        	<div class="flex-description"><p>In the schools within the College of Architecture, Design, and the Arts—the School of Architecture, the School of Art and Art History, the School of Design, and the School of Theatre and Music—a student’s success stems from ongoing collaboration with their advisor. Our advisors are located in the Office of Student Affairs, Jefferson Hall 208—the starting place for all academic inquiries. CADA academic advisors will also refer students to other offices on campus, including the Office of Financial Aid and Scholarships, the Office of the Dean of Students, and other vital resources on the UIC campus.</p>
</div>
        	<!-- End Description -->	

        
